      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward, practical transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who appreciates value, simplicity, and the opportunity to own a vehicle without a major upfront cost. A sensible choice for commuting, a backup car, or a project for the right owner.",
