    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car that can still get the job done? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants simple transportation or a great little project to tinker with. It has the kind of character you\u2019d expect from a well-used vehicle, and for the money, it offers a lot of value. If you want something inexpensive with potential, this is well worth a look.",
