      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with good bones and a drivetrain that still pulls cleanly. Not a showroom piece, but it starts, drives, and offers a solid platform for someone who wants dependable transportation or an easy project. The engine feels responsive, the transmission does its job, and it has the kind of straightforward, mechanical character that makes these worth keeping on the road. Cosmetically it shows age and use, but for the money you\u2019re getting an affordable, usable vehicle with plenty of life left for the next owner. Priced to move.",
